'''[[科威特|科威特]]的女同性恋、男同性恋、双性恋和跨性别群體（[[LGBT|LGBT]]）'''面临着法律和社会的諸多挑战。該國对同性恋没有特别的禁令，但其可能因触犯《放荡法》而被起诉。LGBT群體面临着政府的定期起诉、被其他人视为耻辱等。

==法律==
科威特《刑法》包含一些禁止[[情欲|放荡]]和不道德行为的一般规定，可用来惩罚LGBT人群。

*《刑法》第193条惩罚“成年男子（21岁以上）之间的自愿性交”，最高可判处7年监禁。<ref>{{cite web |title=ILGA State Sponsored Homophobia 2019 |url=https://ilga.org/downloads/ILGA_State_Sponsored_Homophobia_2019.pdf |accessdate=2020-11-04 |archive-date=2019-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222220100/https://ilga.org/downloads/ILGA_State_Sponsored_Homophobia_2019.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 第198条禁止公众不道德行为。2008年，该法律得到了扩展，还宣布禁止“模仿异性成员的外貌”，并处以罚款和/或监禁。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gulfnews.com/world/gulf/kuwait/cross-dressers-heads-shaved-in-kuwait-1.1880480|title=Cross-dressers' heads shaved in Kuwait|website=gulfnews.com|language=en|access-date=2019-06-26|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626075916/https://gulfnews.com/world/gulf/kuwait/cross-dressers-heads-shaved-in-kuwait-1.1880480|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年9月，有消息称所有[[海湾阿拉伯国家合作委员会|海湾合作国家]]都同意讨论一项提议，即建立某种形式但未知的测试，以禁止外国同性恋者进入任何国家。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lgbtweekly.com/2013/10/08/gulf-cooperation-countries-to-test-detect-then-ban-gays-from-entering-their-countries/|title=Gulf Cooperation Countries to test, detect then ban gays from entering their countries|website=LGBTWeekly.com|access-date=2018-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131008205203/http://lgbtweekly.com/2013/10/08/gulf-cooperation-countries-to-test-detect-then-ban-gays-from-entering-their-countries/|archive-date=2013-10-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/09/gulf-countries-detect-gays_n_4065927.html|title=Gulf Countries Propose Test To 'Detect' Gays, Ban Them From Entering|publisher=Huffington Post|author=Cavan Sieczkowski|date=2013-09-10|accessdate=2015-08-14|archive-date=2017-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171103134505/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/09/gulf-countries-detect-gays_n_4065927.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，有人认为，对在[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]]举办[[2022年國際足協世界盃|2022年國際足協世界盃]]的担忧，以及对足球迷可能会被审查的争议的担心，使得官员们收回了计划，并坚称这只是一个提议。<ref>{{cite web|title=Kuwaiti authorities arrest 23 'cross-dressers and homosexuals'|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/kuwaiti-authorities-arrest-23-cross-dressers-and-homosexuals-106994114|website=Middle East Eye|date=2015-02-13|access-date=2016-05-31|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629102738/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/kuwaiti-authorities-arrest-23-cross-dressers-and-homosexuals-106994114|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年，波兰[[Instagram|Instagram]]紅人King Luxy因涉嫌过于女性化而在科威特被捕，隨後被关押了两个星期。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/blog/2017/9/15/kuwaiti-police-arrest-abuse-feminine-instagram-star|title=This controversial Instagram star was arrested and abused for being 'too feminine' in Kuwait|last=Arab|first=The New|website=alaraby|language=en|access-date=2019-06-26|archive-date=2019-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508104252/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/blog/2017/9/15/kuwaiti-police-arrest-abuse-feminine-instagram-star|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==HIV/AIDS议题==
1988年，科威特公共卫生部发表了一份关于科威特艾滋病毒感染的报告<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gateway.nlm.nih.gov/MeetingAbstracts/102181265.html |title=A survey for unrecognized HIV infection in a special STD clinic in Kuwait |publisher=Gateway.nlm.nih.gov |date= |accessdate=2011-01-20 |archive-date=2007-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715135159/http://gateway.nlm.nih.gov/MeetingAbstracts/102181265.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，特别是感染人群的国籍，婚姻状况和性取向。2004年，联合国在科威特的一份关于艾滋病毒的报告发现，已知传播病例中约有6％是男性之间无保护的性接触的结果。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.data.unaids.org/Publications/Fact-Sheets01/kuwait_en.pdf|title=Kuwait|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070703224611/http://data.unaids.org/Publications/Fact-Sheets01/kuwait_en.pdf|archivedate=2007-07-03|dead-url=yes|accessdate=2007-08-21}}</ref>

1992年，科威特[[国民议会_(科威特)|国民议会]]宣布有意将傳染[[艾滋病毒|艾滋病毒]]给他人視為非法。

==LGBT权利运动==
科威特没有已知的协会或慈善机构为LGBT权利开展运动或组织LGBT社区的教育和社交活动。

2007年，[[阿拉伯卫星电视台|阿拉伯卫星电视台]]报道说，一群科威特人已申请许可，成立了一个新协会，以捍卫[[LGBT|LGBT]]科威特人的权利。所有这些利益集团或俱乐部都必须得到劳工和社会事务部的批准，该部从未正式答复过。

该组织于2019年7月宣布，他们将再次向商务部申请许可证，以应对商务部对代表同性恋的符号（如商店中的彩虹）进行镇压的行为。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2019/8/1/kuwaits-gay-community-wants-official-recognition-for-lgbt-rights|title=Kuwait's gay community wants official recognition for LGBT rights|last=Arab|first=The New|website=alaraby|language=en|access-date=2020-03-11|archive-date=2019-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190801163453/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2019/8/1/kuwaits-gay-community-wants-official-recognition-for-lgbt-rights|dead-url=no}}</ref>

